name: CDP-diacylglycerol---glycerol-3-phosphate 1-phosphatidyltransferase
classes: Transferases for other substituted phosphate groups
comment: The enzyme catalyses the committed step in the biosynthesis of acidic phospholipids known by the common names phophatidylglycerols and cardiolipins.
